pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `employee` ( `employeeid` int(25) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `phone` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `id` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `password` varchar(25) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`employeeid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `employee_resume` ( `pid` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `id` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `pic` longtext NOT NULL, `name` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `phone` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `address` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `course` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `school` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `CGPA` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `year` varchar(4) NOT NULL, `org` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `des` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `dur1` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `dur2` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `employ` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `workrole` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `in1` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `in2` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `in3` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `skill` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `strength` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `ptitle` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `pdesc` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `pdate1` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `pdate2` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `prole` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `otitle` varchar(2555) NOT NULL, `odesc` varchar(4000) NOT NULL, `rname` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `rdes` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `rorg` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `rphone` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `remail` varchar(40) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`pid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=20 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `employer` ( `employerid` int(25) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `cname` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `cphone` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `cemail` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `caddress` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `cid` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `cpsw` varchar(40) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`employerid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `vacancy` ( `vid` int(100) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `cid` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `cname` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `cphone` varchar(16) NOT NULL, `cemail` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `jlocation` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `jobtitle` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `jreq` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `jdesc` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `jdate` varchar(25) NOT NULL, `jsalary` varchar(25) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`vid`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=27 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
